A day in Portugal  #01

"As I walk by the lanes of ancient building
I see beyond mere buildings
A story cemented over centuries
Unheard, untold, hidden in history

As I walk by the lanes,
I see emotions carved in various forms
Some speak of civilization
Some speak of  downfall
Some speak of evolution
Some speak of timelessness

As I walk by the lanes, 
I see stories hidden behind those wall "

-sigmax
